item.title: CVE-2020-6210|2024-08-04T08:55:21.854Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20fiori%20launchpad
item.description: SAP Fiori Launchpad, versions- 753, 754, does not sufficiently encode user-controlled inputs, and hence allowing the attacker to inject the meta tag into the launchpad html using the vulnerable parameter, leading to reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.
